#### **2. üîß Service ‚Üí Repository**
```java
// Nel HabitService
public Habit createHabit(HabitBuilder builder) {
    Habit habit = builder.build();

    // Validazione business logic
    Optional<Habit> existing = habitRepository.findByUserIdAndName(
        habit.getUserId(), habit.getName());

    if (existing.isPresent()) {
        throw new DuplicateHabitException("Abitudine gi√† esistente");
    }

    // Salva tramite repository
    return habitRepository.save(habit);
}
```

#### **3. üíæ Repository ‚Üí Database**
```java
